154
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:52,720
Strategi militernya belum tentu
kalah dari Kaisar Liyang.

155
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:55,879
Bibi, tenang saja.

156
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,200
